events.title: SmartWorld
events.description: An event conducted by IEEE SCT SB where you will learn the steps involved in the making of Filament bulb. It is a one day workshop conducted in aassociation with the electronics department of our college.

events.title: FlutterForward
events.description: An event conducted by GDSC Pranav sama where you will begin your first steps in app development using the Flutter. Pranav is an intern in a company called trizlabs where he develops user interface for his clients.Enjoy your journey through the world of flutter and dart.
